scripts.comment: 在 OLED SSD1306 上连续显示旋转编码器的位置值 - 按下时重置位置 continuosly show the position value of rotary encoder on OLED SSD1306 - reset the position when pressed

注意：由于所使用的实现方式，每转可能错过几步，而不是每转精确 40步。因此，不要使用它来跟踪旋钮的绝对位置，只需使用旋转编码器返回的位置值即可知道旋钮顺时针或逆时针转动了多少 Note : instead of exactly 40 step per turn, several steps may be missed per turn due to the implementation used. So do not use it to track the absolute position of the knob, just use the position value return by the rotary encoder know the knob have been turn CW or CCW by how much
持续显示旋转编码器的位置值 - 按下时重置位置 continuosly show the position value of rotary encoder - reset the position when pressed
使用此图块重置旋转编码器的位置 use this block to reset the position of the Rotary Encoder
当旋转编码器 EC11 按下时，其行为类似于按钮 - KEY 是按钮的输出 - 通常为低 - 按下时为高 when rotary encoder EC11 behave like a push button when pressed - KEY is output of the push button - normally LOW - HIGH when pressed

Status 将返回旋转编码器的当前位置 - 每转 40 步 - 顺时针将增加值 - 逆时针将减少值 Status will return the current position of the rotary encoder - 40 steps every turn - clockwise (CW) will increase the value - counter-clockwise (CCW) will decrease the value
需要初始化旋转编码器 - 如果旋转方向错误，只需交换 S1 和 S2 接线 need to initialize the rotary encoder - if rotation is wrong direction, just swap the S1 & S2 wiring
EC11 旋转编码器引脚连接 EC11 Rotary Encoder pin connection - GND : GND - S1 : GPIO13 - S2 : GPIO12 - KEY : GPIO14 - 5V : 3.3V or 5V
验证与 espSnap 的连接 verify connection to espSnap

使用它来停止检查旋转编码器的旋转 - 仅当同一引脚用于其他用途且未关闭电源或重置 espSnap 时才需要这样做 use this to stop checking of rotary encoder rotation - this is only required if the same pin is used for other purpose without power off or reset of espSnap
